IOT-Based Multimode Robot-M3R is a robot car with 3 modes
mode1: Obstacle avoidance mode. Robot moves in an obstacle-less path
mode2: In this mode, robot car control is given to the user i.e. Remote car.
Mode3: In this mode, the robot follows an object in front of it.
Robot car is controlled through the Blynk app by switching of modes, using it like a remote car, etc.
